  "text": "Othmers then coupled lefthemisphere training in the beta1 band with SMR training of the right sensorimotor strip in order to address both the left and right hemisphere aspects of the depressive syndrome. By 1997 the training had moved off the sensorimotor strip to engage the prefrontal region with Fp1-C3 for improved activation, and the parietal region with C4-Pz for right-hemisphere overarousal [CITATION_1] .",
